basic.abilityDesc: The Pokemon heals up to 1/4 of its maximum Hit Points when hit with Electric-type moves.

basic.name: Meltan
basic.description: It dissolves and eats metal. Circulating liquid metal within its body is how it generates energy.
basic.abilityDesc: Steel types cannot run nor switch while this Pokemon is in battle. Because the opponent's switching is blocked, the opponent cannot switch on the turn this Pokemon switches out of battle. The opponent may still switch with Baton Pass.
basic.hiddenAbilityDesc: None
